quran[3{c,v,t}:
2,246,"phir tum ne uss muamlay par bhi ghhor kya, jo( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)ke baad sardaraan bani Israel ko paish aaya tha? onhon ne apne nabi se kaha : hamaray liye aik badshah muqarrar kar do taakay hum Allah ki raah mein jung karen nabi ne poocha : kahin aisa to nah hoga ke tum ko larai ka hukum diya jaye aur phir tum nah lrho woh kehnay lagey : bhala yeh kaisay ho sakta hai ke hum raah khuda mein nah lrhin, jabkay hamein apne gharon se nikaal diya gaya hai aur hamaray baal bachay hum se judda kar diye gay hain magar jab un ko jung ka hukum diya gaya, to aik qaleel tadaad ke siwa woh sab peeth mourr gay, aur Allah un mein se aik aik zalim ko jaanta hai"
2,247,"unn ke nabi ne un se kaha ke Allah ne Taloot ko tumahray liye badshah muqarrar kya hai yeh sun kar woh bolay :"" hum par badshah ban'nay ka woh kaisay haqdaar ho gaya? uss ke muqablay mein badshahi ke hum ziyada mustahiq hain woh to koi bara ma l- daar aadmi nahi hai"" nabi ne jawab diya :"" Allah ne tumahray muqablay mein isi ko muntakhib kya hai aur is ko dimaghi o jismani dono qisam ki ahliyaten farawani ke sath ataa farmai hain aur Allah ko ikhtiyar hai ke apna malik jisay chahay day, Allah barri wusat rakhta hai aur sab kuch uss ke ilm mein hai """
2,248,"is ke sath unn ke nabi ne unn ko yeh bhi bataya ke"" khuda ki taraf se uss ke badshah muqarrar honay ki alamat yeh hai ke is ke ehad mein woh sandooq tumhe wapas mil jaye ga, jis mein tumahray Rab ki taraf se tumahray liye sukoon qalb ka samaan hai, jis mein all( hazrat ) Moose(alh-e-salam)aur all Haroon ke chhorey hue tabarruqaat hain, aur jis ko is waqt farishtay sambhale hue hain agar tum momin ho, to yeh tumahray liye bohat barri nishani hai"
